name: HORDE TANK #13
description:
When an alien virus infected the world humans and machines bonded. We escaped into the virtual world to fight for our existence. This is new URTH an original series featuring an array of original characters. The Horde has created savage monster machines to lay waste to their opposition.

By holding a character in this series you are eligible for secret airdrops. Collect and hold all of the characters for a chance to get the original comic when it’s released. Copyright @smileghostnft
To find out more about my creations follow me on Twitter @smileghostnft and check out the site at www.smileghost.com
